unittitle.value: Hisham Khatib Collection - A tour of Palestine, 1903.

p.value: 2,930 photographs and postcards (both individual prints and contained within albums) focussed on the Near East, including the Holy Land, Palestine, Jordan, Turkey, Syria and Egypt as well as a very small number from Europe.
